Package: drawSEM
Title: Interactive Visual Model Editor for Structural Equation Modeling, starting with OpenMx
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Timothy R. Brick <tbrick@psu.edu>
Maintainer: Timothy R. Brick <tbrick@psu.edu>
Description: Interactive visual tool for building structural equation models (SEMs) 
  in OpenMx (and eventually lavaan and blavaan). Edit models graphically, validate schemas, 
  and export to R objects to run.
